data.description: Escape to your own sanctuary located in a 24 hr guard gated, golf & tennis community. Stunning 4 bdrm, 5 bath retreat, designed to capture the essence of coastal living. Step inside to discover a spacious interior, with tons of natural light. Updated kitchen features quartz countertops, premium appliances & ample storage. The primary suite offers a private haven w/spa-like ensuite bathroom & walk-in closet.  Additional features - hurricane impact windows & doors, wired stand by generator, wired speakers inside & out, fireplace, laundry room w/sink & vanity & 3 car garage. Boasting serene pool & garden views, the expansive patio beckons for leisure & entertaining. Custom landscaping creating a lush & tranquil oasis. Schedule your preview today!
